Articles.Content:
No matter what i do, fresh install, no mods. Or jam packed with mods, running both x64 and x86 builds of 1.1.2 i get this error and im sick of it! It happens every 5 minutes and has rendered the game completely unplayable. I cant make it though a launch or reentry without having at least 3 crashes. 

Don't get me wrong i love the game, but this kind of issue is making me seriously consider quitting. Please help me. Please see the spoiler for my output log from the most recent crash in x64 mode. Only mods installed are KJR,Mechjeb2 and ModManager. This error happens regardless of mods however.
